msgid "Scenario I–B: Return to The House Always Wins"
msgstr "冒险I–B：重返百赌百胜"

msgid "Choose one of the two Clover Club Lounge locations at random. Put the chosen location into play, and remove the other version from the game. Then, put the Clover Club Bar, Clover Club Cardroom, and La Bella Luna locations into play. Each investigator begins play in La Bella Luna."
msgstr "随机选择2个俱乐部大厅地点之一。将所选地点放置入场，并把另一个版本的俱乐部大厅地点移出游戏。然后，将俱乐部酒吧、俱乐部卡牌室、月下美人放置入场。每位调查员从月下美人开始游戏。"

msgid "Set the following cards aside, out of play: Clover Club Stage, Darkened Hall, Peter Clover, Dr. Francis Morgan, and each copy of Back Hall Doorway."
msgstr "将下列卡牌放在一边，位于场外：俱乐部舞台、黑暗走廊、彼得·克劳佛、佛朗西斯·摩尔根博士，以及所有走廊后门。"
